  "title": "Marine service engineer",
  "description": "<p>We have an excellent opportunity for young and energetic field engineers holding Electronic &amp; Telecommunication background.</p>\n<p><u>Job Responsibilities:</u></p>\n<p>· Provide repair, maintenance, commissioning of marine navigation and communication equipment.</p>\n<p>· To study job inquiries from customer and prepare accordingly.</p>\n<p>· To prepare service report after service / commissioning.</p>\n<p>· To work according to company's Safety Regulations at all workplace.</p>\n<p><u>Job Requirements:</u></p>\n<p>· Min ITE/ Diploma in Electronics &amp; Telecommunication Engineering</p>\n<p>· Min 2 years’ experience hands-on experience in marine electronics industry</p>\n<p>· Good interaction and communication skills.</p>\n<p>· Able to travel oversea when needed Able to work irregular hours.</p>\n<p>Entry Level candidates with no experience are welcome to apply, on job training will be provided.</p>",
